	<h1>USIDK-BUILD</h1>

	<h2>What is UISDK-build?</h2>
	<p> 
		<ul>
			<li>it's a lightweight Node.js application that performs common build phases for web application projects</li>
			<li>command line based tool</li>
			<li>encapsulates set of features to support large scale JavaScript applications</li>
		</ul>
	</p>
