	<h2>Why use UISDK-build?</h2>
	<p>
	UISDK-build has multiple features useful when building web application projects:
	</p>
	<ul>
		<li>easy and intuitive to use</li>
		<li>lightweight</li>
		<li>extendable (modular architecture accomodates changes easily)</li>
		<li>javascript oriented</li>
		<li>globaly configurable (using JSON notation)</li>
		<li>simple command line interface</li>
		<li>embedded help</li>
